citysdk.tourism.client.poi.single
Class HypermediaLink

java.lang.Object
  citysdk.tourism.client.poi.single.HypermediaLink

public class HypermediaLink
extends java.lang.Object

A HypermediaLink is a link in which a given client can make REST HTTP requests.

It is composed of

  • a version;
  • the available hypermedia links;
Some terminologies can be found in ParameterTerms (for parameters) and ResourceTerms (for resources)

Pedro Cruz
